\name 
showmsg - show persistent messages
\synopsis
showmsg [all]
\description
Allows you to display your persistent private messages.
the lines count is defined by msg_display_count.
"all" can by used to display all your messages without lines count limit
\example
> showmessage
Your message(s) :
1 27/05/2003 21:55:35 Root : Is there anybody out there? 
You have 1 message
\see also 
sendmsg, clearmsg
